text: Cruiser 'Varyag' () is a 1946 Soviet war movie directed by Viktor Eisymont.От блокады до «Варяга». Лучшие фильмы режиссера Виктора Эйсымонта It stars Boris Livanov, Aleksandr Zrazhevsky, and Nikolai Chaplygin. == Actors == * Boris Livanov as Rudnev * Aleksandr Zrazhevsky as Belyaev * Nikolai Chaplygin as Bobylev * Vyacheslav Novikov as Antonych * Vsevolod Larionov as Dorofeyev * Georgy Petrovsky as Pavlov == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1946 war movies Category:Soviet war movies Category:Movies directed by Viktor Eisymont
title: Cruiser 'Varyag'
